name: Orchidée Impériale Black The Cream (Refill)
short_description:
fter more than 15 years of research, the Orchidarium and Guerlain Research present Orchidée Impériale Black The Cream, a masterpiece of Guerlain skincare featuring the extraordinary properties of the Black Orchid. Originally from Peru, this rare orchid increases its longevity by adapting to its environment. Like a talisman in the combat against time, the Black Orchid has given rise to the BlackimmuneTM technology, Each application helps the skin better withstand internal and external stresses and reduce the visible signs of ageing. The Cream helps minimize wrinkles, refine the skin texture and lend definition to facial contours, leaving the skin feeling firmer and suppler as well as looking radiant.

The refill comes in a gem of a porcelain jar hand-crafted by Maison Bernardaud, the prestigious maker of Limoges porcelain. Designed for travelling, the refill is easy to remove from the jar. The refillable format demonstrates Guerlain’s commitment to a more sustainable approach to luxury.

name: [Mini] Black Tea Firming Overnight Mask
short_description:
Fresh Black Tea Firming Overnight Mask is an intensely moisturizing treatment that lifts your nighttime ritual to new heights. This sleeping mask acts like a corset for your complexion, giving you a lifted, firmer look by morning.

A proprietary complex of kombucha (black tea ferment), black tea extract, blackberry leaf extract, and lychee seed extract is proven to inhibit damaging free radicals and helps improve the appearance of skin elasticity. The overnight mask also features belle de nuit extract to soothe and rebalance the skin, peptides to help firm the skin and visibly defy the signs of gravity, and hyaluronic acid to attract and maintain moisture to enhance suppleness.

name: [Mini] Vitamin Nectar Vibrancy-Boosting Face Mask
short_description: Get glowing skin instantly with Fresh Vitamin Nectar Vibrancy-Boosting Face Mask. This powerhouse treatment improves the skin's radiance and glow by 31 percent after one use, and by 49 percent after four weeks of use. The revolutionary formula is powered by 50 percent real crushed citrus fruits including oranges, lemons, and clementines, naturally containing AHA fruit acids that work to gently refine and smooth the skin. This fruit blend comes in the form of a paste, which is made from lemons cultivated in the Mediterranean region—providing double exfoliation by offering a pleasant scrub, while the AHA fruit acid content offers a chemical peeling effect. A proprietary vitamin fruit complex is a potent blend of vitamins, citrus fruit extracts, and minerals that help revitalize dull skin for a vibrant, healthy-looking glow and soft, smooth texture.

name: Hangover Replenishing Face Primer
short_description:
Got a beauty hangover? Too Faced's replenishing face primer is your instant cure. It hydrates, smoothes and brightens skin for a dewy, healthy looking finish.

When long days of work and late nights of play give you a beauty hangover, this is your instant cure. Hangover is a revolutionary makeup primer infused with coconut water, probiotics and skin revivers that work together to boost skin's radiance, promote elasticity and help hydrate while locking down makeup for fresher, longer and more flawless wear.

Too Faced harnessed the science of hydration to create a creamy, penetrating primer that acts like an energy drink for the skin by replenishing moisture levels. It can be worn alone for a dewy, healthy looking finish or under bronzers, foundations and powders to create the perfect canvas.

More To Love:
Hydrate and brighten skin
Promote skin's elasticity and tone
Soothe and smooth the skin
Get all the priming benefits you love while looking like you received eight hours of sleep and drank your daily dose of H2O
Paraben free
Cruelty free
Vegan friendly

name: Hangover Good To Go Skin Protecting Moisturizer SPF25
short_description:
Hangover Good to Go Skin Protecting SPF 25 Moisturizer protects, giving you the hydrated, glowing complexion you want while shielding you from harmful UVA/UVB rays with broad-spectrum SPF 25 protection. This lightweight, dewy moisturizer is your daily source of antioxidants, vitamin-enriched moisture, and sun protection.

Too Faced has taken the replenishing and soothing essence of their iconic Hangover Primer to the next level with this lightweight moisturizer with a heavyweight defense created specifically to hydrate and protect your skin while helping your makeup look better.

The formula is infused with a blend of nature¿s hydrators, along with skin loving ingredients like Cinnamon Bark extract, Jojoba Oil, Aloe Vera extract, coconut water, and skin care star Hyaluronic Acid to help nourish skin. The powerful non-greasy formula, with vitamins E, C, and pre-and-probiotic-based ingredients, provides broad-spectrum UVA/UVB SPF 25 protection.

Benefits:
Moisturizes and deeply nourishes skin
Gives skin a luminous glow
Creates a soft, smooth canvas perfect for makeup
Broad-spectrum UVA/UVB protection helps prevent dark spots and discoloration from forming
Broad-spectrum UVA/UVB protection helps prevent the sun's rays from breaking down natural collagen
Absorbs quickly into skin
No white residue, suitable for all skin tones
Can be used all over face
Smells like coconut water
Cruelty free

name: Hangover 3-In-1 Replenishing Primer & Setting Spray
short_description:
A weightless 3-in-1 mist that primes, sets and refreshes makeup while it helps keep skin hydrated. This super-hydrating, multitasking mist is infused with coconut water and can be used as a primer before makeup, a setting spray to keep makeup in place all day and a midday refresher anytime your skin needs a boost, serving as the perfect cure for a beauty hangover. The unique combination of coconut water, probiotic-based ingredients and skin revivers works to hydrate and brighten skin, promote skin's elasticity and tone and soothe and smooth the skin.

How to use:
Shake well; hold bottle 6-8 inches away from face; mist directly onto skin
Prime - Apply to clean skin before makeup
Set - Apply after makeup to keep it in place all day
Refresh - Use anytime to refresh skin
Cruelty-Free

name: Correct & Perfect All-In-One Color Correcting Palette
short_description:
Create Complexion Perfection!

Under-eye circles, redness, uneven or dull skin? Not anymore with this all-in-one customizable color correcting palette. Five velvety smooth cream color correctors and two tinted setting powders are all you need to help neutralize imperfections and brighten dull skin tones.

Cream Correctors:

Peach – neutralizes dark under-eye circles on fair/medium skin tones
Pink – brightens eye area and masks fatigue
Yellow – neutralizes hyperpigmentation and dark spots
Green – counteracts redness (i.e. from rosacea, acne, broken capillaries, and sunburn)
Orange – counteracts dark under-eye circles on darker skin tones; also neutralizes veins

Pressed Setting Powders: 

Yellow – sets any correcting cream or can be used allover to even out skin tone
Lavender – sets pink correcting cream or can be used allover to brighten sallow/yellow skin


Benefits:

Five lightweight, sheer to medium, buildable colored creams and two tinted translucent finishing powders allow for customized coverage.
Specially formulated with nourishing vitamins A, C and E and Arclay Youth Revival Bio-Available Mineral Complex™ to help diminish the appearance of pores and fine lines, moisturize and control oil
Long-wearing, waterproof
Easy to master! Includes a user-friendly booklet filled with makeup artist inspired tips and tricks.

name: Le Lift Hand Cream
short_description:
A restoring hand cream that nourishes skin and helps maintain beautiful hands, which often show the first signs of aging. Featuring a comforting, quick-absorbing texture, the formula leaves hands feeling smooth, soft and replenished.

WHAT IT DOES:
The nourishing texture of LE LIFT LA CREME MAIN envelops skin, leaving hands delicately scented with a velvety-soft feel; an unprecedented sensorial experience
KEY INGREDIENTS:
LE LIFT LA CREME MAIN combines botanical alfalfa concentrate (a gentle ingredient as efficient as retinol) with natural licorice extract to help visibly smooth the appearance of wrinkles and even skin tone
Alfalfa is a 1,000-year-old plant known for its remineralizing and nutritional benefits; rich in minerals and trace elements, alfalfa is grown organically in France for optimal quality
Like retinol (a key ingredient against skin aging), botanical alfalfa concentrate helps renew the look of skin and increase firmness

This unique blend of powders provides a smooth, even, flawless finish. Witch Hazel and Licorice Extract prime skin for makeup by minimizing the appearance of pores and evening skin tone.

Starting at the center of the face in a downward sweeping motion, apply LE BLANC DE CHANEL to the forehead, cheeks, nose and chin with a combination of fingers, Foundation Brush #6 or a sponge. Can be worn alone, under foundation or on top for a fresh, radiant result.

A quick-absorbing eye cream with moisturizers that melt onto the skin. This cult-favorite cream leaves the eye area soft, smooth, and refreshed. Who It's For: Anyone looking for a lightweight, soothing eye cream to wear on its own or layered under concealer for a flawless finish.

WHO IT'S FOR:
Anyone looking for a lightweight, soothing eye cream to wear on its own or layered under concealer for a flawless finish.
KEY INGREDIENTS:
Formulated with our signature Enriched Mineral Water Blend to hydrate, balance and revive skin.
Aloe Vera and Witch Hazel extract, Jojoba Seed, Avocado Oil, and Squalane help skin feel comforted and conditioned.
HOW TO USE:
Apply with fingers, patting gently around eye area.
Make sure cream is fully absorbed before applying Concealer.

name: Terracotta Matte Sculpting Powder
short_description:
This sun-kissed powder warms the complexion and sculpts the features. Soft and easy to apply, its comfortable, ultra-fine texture blends with the skin to build the result up to the desired intensity. Enriched with Kaolin, a white clay known for its mattifying properties, the matte powder sculpts the complexion with a shine-free finish.
How To Apply Sculpting Powder: Apply the sculpting powder with a brush, tracing a "3" on each side of the face, from the forehead to just under the cheekbones, from under the cheekbones to the chin, finishing with a stroke down the neck.

name: Ultra Repair Hydrating Serum
short_description:
INSTANTLY HYDRATE, PLUMP & SMOOTH


A universal serum that gives skin its daily dose of moisture for soft, smooth, youthful-looking skin. Formulated for all skin types, this hydrating gel instantly infuses skin with essential hydration to help plump and minimize the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles.

This water-based gel absorbs immediately into the skin leaving behind an invisible shield that helps to seal in hydration. Its lightweight texture makes it perfect for layering under your favorite A.M. and P.M. moisturizers. Hyaluronic Acida moisture-locking agenthelps hydrate, plump and nourish. Anti-aging Peptides help minimize the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles, while Collagen helps skin appear more plump and replenished with an improved-looking texture. Colloidal Oatmeal, along with Aloe Leaf Juice, help calm and soothe irritated skin for an allover healthy-looking and feeling complexion.

name: Precisely, My Brow Pencil Ultra-Fine Brow Defining Pencil
short_description:
Transform shapeless, undefined brows with just a few strokes of Benefit's bestselling precisely, my brow pencil. The custom ultra-fine tip makes adding detailed definition to your brows easy, by drawing incredibly natural-looking, hair like strokes that last up to 12-hours.* This rich, waterproof** eyebrow pencil is ideal for spot filling sparse or over-tweezed areas, and the smudge-proof formula is firm enough for precise application, yet glides on effortlessly to bring symmetry to your brows and your entire face.

How to Apply:
Hold the pencil along the custom control grip
To shape brows, use longer, horizontal strokes along the base of your brow
Fill by drawing short, upward strokes in the direction of your natural hair growth
Gently brush through brows with the Spoolie to evenly blend color & tame hairs

name: Born This Way Foundation
short_description:
Too Faced Born This Way Undetectable Medium-to-Full Coverage Foundation is an oil-free foundation offering medium-to-full natural coverage.

Inspired by "I woke up like this" perfection, Too Faced Co-founder and Chief Creative Officer Jerrod Blandino set out on a mission to create a foundation so undetectable you can go ahead and lie with beautifully natural coverage that will have everyone thinking you were Born This Way.

Infused with:
Coconut Water: Aids in delicately replenishing skin's moisture levels
Alpine Rose: Helps empower skin's health and resilience
Hyaluronic Acid: Gives a smoother, more youthful appearance

This oil-free foundation masterfully diffuses the line between makeup and skin.

Coverage so undetectable, they'll think you were Born This Way.

name: H.A. INTENSIFIER
short_description:
Skinceuticals H.A. Intensifier is a multi-beneficial corrective serum proven to amplify skins hyaluronic acid levels. This unique formulation contains a high concentration of pure hyaluronic acid, proxylane and botanical extracts of licorice root and purple rice to support skins hyaluronic acid levels and deliver surface hydration, helping improve the visible appearance of firmness, smoothness, and facial plumpness. This hyaluronic acid serum may be used as part of a home skincare regimen after dermal fillers; always consult with your physician for individual at-home advice.



  • Amplifies skins hyaluronic acid levels by 30%

  • Reduces the look of crows feet, nasolabial folds (parenthesis around the mouth or laugh lines), and marionette lines (lines from the corners of the mouth down to chin) for smoother, firmer skin

  • Delivers long lasting hydration to visibly improve skins texture

  • Unique serum-gel texture format creates a smooth canvas on skin

  • Tightens, firms, and lifts loose, sagging skin

The Vinosource Serum captures and continually diffuses water with intensity to restore skins moisture balance and to leave it feeling supple and fresh.

Thanks to a combination of different intelligent rehydrating active ingredients, this serum stimulates the internal hydration mechanisms, regulates water flow and restores the skin water balance. Immediately, the skin feels as if drenched in water, plump and springy. Replenished and soothed, your skin regains long-lasting suppleness, softness, and well-being.

Its ultra-light and fresh aqueous texture melts under your fingers.

The ultra-light aqueous texture absorbs quickly into the skin for immediate results.

A light fragrance with citrus notes on a refreshing bouquet: mandarin blossom, lemon tree leaves, cucumber water and fresh mint

Benefits :
Captures and continuously diffuses water
Restores balance and moisture to the skin
Rehydrates & refreshes

name: Rouge Coco Lip Blush Hydrating Lip And Cheek Sheer Colour Teasing Pink
short_description:
CHANEL introduces ROUGE COCO LIP BLUSH.
A touch of subtle colour for the lips, a flash of emotion for the cheeks.
Its 2-in-1 gel formula leaves a delicate coloured halo on the cheeks, while its ultra-lightweight, comfortable and non-sticky texture moisturises and softens the lips.
A silky and luminous sensation on application that melts away to leave a soft, airy caress on the lips with a matte effect.


How to use



On lips: apply a thin layer in one stroke, using the flat part of the applicator for the lower lip and the tip for the upper lip.
On cheeks: smile to define the apples of your cheeks. Dot 1 to 3 times onto cheeks, depending on the desired intensity, and blend the colour with fingertips

short_description:
A versatile eyeshadow palette for easy, neutral-toned looks.


Five smudgeproof, long-lasting colors from soft to intense, with matte to shimmery finishes, offer a base, highlighter and liner effects. It includes a soft-hair brush applicator for smooth, optimal application.

name: Hydra Beauty Micro Serum Intense Replenishing Hydration
short_description:
A water-light serum that delivers a revolutionary infusion of hydration 24 hours of continuous moisturizing benefits leaving skin deeply replenished, smooth and glowing with youth.


hydration is increased by 33% and intensely plumped by 32% (both based on an instrumental evaluation of 22 women after 28 days of use). Patented micro-droplet technology protects the purity of ultra-moisturizing Camellia Alba OFA (oleofractioned active and a highly concentrated form of camellia oil extract) until the very moment of application. Upon release, Camellia Alba OFA provides replenishment and an intense plumping effect. Camellia Alba PFA (polyfractioned active, an ultra-pure, ultra-powerful ingredient created through exclusive patented CHANEL technology) works to maintain skins optimal moisture levels while the powerful antioxidant Blue Ginger PFA helps to protect and reinforce skin's natural defense system.


Apply in the morning and evening to a cleansed and toned face and neck before your moisturizer Ideal for dry, normal, combination or oily skin types.

name: All Nighter Ultra Matte Setting Spray
short_description:
A weightless setting spray that locks makeup in place while absorbing oil on the skin's surface and controlling shine for an ultra-matte finish that lasts up to 16 hours.

All Nighter Ultra Matte Setting Sprays micro fine mist refreshes skin while mattifying and setting your look. No makeup meltdowns here Ultra Matte's breathable formula keeps makeup looking shine-free and fresh for up to 16 hours without fading or settling into fine lines. So sweat, get wet, and go to the after party no touch-ups needed.

If you see white droplets on your skin after you spray, thats just the kaolin clay and ultra-mattifying effect at work! Shake the bottle 5 times to activate the formula, then prime it by pressing fully down on the pump and spraying it in the air a few times. This ensures even and translucent application.

name: ALL NIGHTER SETTING SPRAY
short_description:
Is makeup meltdown ruining your midnight mojo? Mist on this weightless spray to give your makeup serious staying power. All Nighter Makeup Setting Spray keeps makeup looking gorgeously just-applied for up to 16 hours without melting, fading or settling into fine lines.

Developed in an exclusive partnership with Skindinavia, our groundbreaking, tested formula is suitable for all skin types, free of oil and parabens, and features patented Temperature Control Technology. Yep, this baby actually lowers the temperature of your makeup to keep foundation, eyeshadow, blush and concealer in place even in hot and humid or cold and windy conditions. The result? Smoother-looking skin and vibrant makeup that lasts all day (or all night).

Each shade is laced with micro-fine sparkle and lush 3D metallic glitter for a luxe, diamond-like effect. Rose-hued shades like Sugar High and Long Night create a subtle flush, while the silver and gold metallics of Neon Moon and No Shame add an icy pop to inner corners.

name: Naked Honey Eyeshadow Palette
short_description:
Meet the Naked Honey Eyeshadow Palette, our newest addition to the Naked family raw and sticky sweet, just the way nature intended. The irresistible combo of retro glam and golden glow makes this the one palette you'll be craving all year. Get hooked on this buzzed-about palette and its 12 exclusive shades; they perfect for creating a swarm of looks, from bright and sunny to dangerously seductive after dark.

Reach for our go-to shade Amber (it practically glows), create the perfect hazy, smoked-out eye with Sting (warm brown matte), or get hooked on Honey (intense gold metallic) for the ultimate  statement eye.

From daytime matte to sultry metallic looks, blending your best look is easy, since the Naked Honey Eyeshadow Palette comes with a vegan and cruelty-free double-ended brush. One end is a smudger brush, which is short and densely packed to apply shadow along the lower lash line or smudge and blend. The other end is a tapered crease brush, perfect for defining the crease and blending shades. You wont find another palette that this sweet.

name: Pure Canvas Primer Hydrating
short_description:
Hydrate and perfect the complexion with Laura Mercier Pure Canvas Primer Hydrating, a replenishing formula that provides rich moisturise and helps to create a flawless base for makeup.


Formulated especially for dry, dehydrated skin, this multitasking primer is lightweight but remarkably moisturising. The gel texture glides easily over the skin, helping to smooth the look of imperfections for a more even complexion.


Vitamins A, C and E provide antioxidant protection while emollient aloe leaf and olive extract condition and soothe dry skin. Apply before foundation to lock in moisture, reduce the appearance of fine lines, wrinkles and redness and to prolong the wear of makeup.






Key Benefits:

  • Hydrating formula nourishes dry skin

  • Vitamin-enriched formula

  • Helps to reduce the appearance of fine lines and redness

  • Use under makeup to extend its wear

  • Contains moisturising plant extracts

  • Lightweight gel texture glides easily over skin

name: Naked Cherry Eyeshadow Palette
short_description:
These 12 all-new shades include of-the-moment soft mattes and sizzling metallics, ranging from creamy ivory and shimmering rose gold to the most intense black cherry.

Because serious staying power and shadow that does not flake or fade out on you are non-negotiables, each shade is made from our mind-blowing formula that gives its velvety texture, rich color and blendability.

Adorned with a row of metallic cherries, the crimson compact includes a full-size mirror and double-sided brush. Ready for precision application on one end and seamless blending on the other. Whether you are at the office, in between flights or getting ready at the apartment, Naked Cherry spices up everything from chill neutrals and sexy shimmers to super smoky eyes.

Shades included:
Hot Spot (ivory matte)

Bang Bang (shimmering pink with gold shift and iridescent micro-sparkle)
Feelz (soft dusty rose matte)
Juicy (soft warm peach)

Ambitious (metallic rose copper)
Bing (deep mauve matte)
Devilish (reddish plum matte)
Young Love (metallic cranberry)
Drunk Dial (deep metallic burgundy)
Privacy (deep brownish-plum matte)

name: Liquid Minerals Foundation - Amber
short_description:
Jane Iredale Liquid Minerals Foundation is a light-reflecting, soft-focus foundation with beads encapsulating skin-nourishing ingredients that work in a time-released action. The spheres include Hyaluronate Acid and Olive Squalene that are entrapped by seaweed lipids, which are then suspended in an Aloe Vera and Lavender Flower gel.


Suitable for all skin types, Jane Iredale Liquid Minerals A Foundation makes skin look more youthful, diminishes the appearance of lines and wrinkles, minimizes pores, and evens out skin tone. It has a natural pH of 6 and is so perfectly balanced that it needs no pH adjusters.


As Jane Iredale Liquid Minerals Foundation is applied and worked into the skin, the body temperature breaks down the liposomes so that they can release their actives in a prolonged time-release action for the ultimate in skin health and protection.

name: No.7 Bonding Oil
short_description:
A first-of-its-kind, highly concentrated, ultra-lightweight, reparative styling oil. Dramatically increase shine, softness, and color vibrancy. Minimizes fly-aways and frizz. Provides heat protection of up to 450 degrees

Hair Type: Straight, Wavy, Curly, and Coily.

Hair Texture: Fine, Medium, and Thick.

Hair Benefits: Protects Colors, Fights Frizz, and Provides Heat Protection.

Formulation: Oil.


Highlighted Ingredients:



  • Bis-aminopropyl Diglycol Dimaleate: works by finding single sulfur hydrogen bonds and cross-linking them back together to form disulfide bonds. Disulfide bonds are broken via chemical, thermal, and mechanical processes including brushing and combing the hair. This gives the hair superior strength by repairing broken disulfide bonds and anti-breakage properties. 

  • Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil: Rich in anti-aging compounds including beta-carotene, vitamins D, C, E, essential fatty acids, and polyphenols to protect and nourish hair.

  • Fermented Green Tea Oil: Nutrition for hair; Korean skincare uses fermented oils due to their superior absorption and performance benefits improves feel, absorption, and compatibility.

short_description:
WHAT IT IS

Hand Care Anti-Aging Concentrate produces a truly complete anti-aging action to protect the handsand rejuvenate them. 2.5 oz. Made in France.

WHAT IT DOES

A high-performance skin care product to fight against visible signs of aging on the hands:wrinkles, dark spots, loss of density and plumpness, skin dryness, etc.

  • 1. It smooths the micro-relief and reduces the appearance of fine lines due to a powerful complexof key ingredients: Lindera extract, Persian Acacia extract, and a Yeast and Soy proteincomplex

  • 2. It visibly reduces the appearance of dark spots due to a powerful skin evening key ingredient, Hexyl Resorcinol. This is combined with two anti-free radical key ingredients (Vitamin E Acetateand Buckwheat seed extract)

  • 4. It provides absolute comfort that is instant and lasting. Silky and melting, its non-greasytexture is rapidly absorbed and leaves a velvety finish on the skin


HOW TO USE IT


Allow to penetrate by lightly massaging into the skin for a transparent and velvety finish.

name: No.3 Hair Perfector
short_description:
OLAPLEX No.3 Hair Perfector is the ultimate breakage insurance. Bring home the salon quality protection of OLAPLEX with this weekly hair strengthening treatment. Featuring a patented active ingredient, OLAPLEX No.3 Hair Perfector works on a molecular level to seek out broken bonds caused by chemical, thermal, and mechanical damage and restores a healthy look and feel to hair.

Key benefits:

Addresses damaged and compromised hair
Strengthens and protects hair structure
Restores healthy appearance and texture


How To Use:
Apply to damp, towel-dried hair from roots to ends
Leave on for at least 10 minutes, then rinse and shampoo as usual
Use 1-3 times per week


Snag the whole Olaplex Hair Perfection Bundle for a complete healthy hair routine.

name: The Longevity Concentrate
short_description:
Guerlain Orchidee Imperiale The Longevity Concentrate has the following features:
It targets the areas where youthful volume has been lost, for redensified, radiant skin.
The highly concentrated Cell RespirationT technology regulates the level of oxygen in the skin cells. The cells can breathe again and maximize energy production which boosts cell regeneration for reducing the signs of ageing.
It also combined with the redensifying action of a natural origin ingredient, tigernut extract which strengthens the structure and cohesion of the fibres supporting the skin.
The skin perfecting effect is down to the action of a rose hip extract that minimizes the pores.

name: Rapid Firm + Lift Treatment Serum Acetyl Hexapeptide-8
short_description:
Estee Lauder Perfectionist Pro Rapid Firm + Lift Treatment Serum Acetyl Hexapeptide-8 has the following features:

Features this high-speed formula that delivers visible improvement to multiple facial zonesalong the jawline, cheeks, around eyes and even stubborn laugh lines for an overall natural, more lifted and youthful look.

Immediately: your skin is radiant, moisturized, rejuvenated.

In just 3 days: your skin feels smooth, plumped, baby-soft. Gentle AHAs refine skin's texture.

In 2 weeks: with a more lifted look and skin feels firmer and facial contours including jawline and cheeks look more lifted and defined.

Lines and wrinkles look dramatically reduced.

Infused with a powerful concentration of Acetyl Hexapeptide-8 a custom-designed rebuilding peptide the formula penetrates quickly.

Helps skin boost its natural collagen and elastin to strengthen its vital support network.

Suitable for all skin types.

name: Velvet Nourishing Cream With Saffron Flowers
short_description:
Sisley Velvet Nourishing Cream With Saffron Flowers has the following features:
Acts against all the causes of skin dryness so that skin instantly and lastingly regains its comfort and beauty.
Protected during the day and repaired at night: during the day, Buckwheat seed extract protects defenceless skin; at night, Shea butter repairs and fortifies skin damaged by outdoor conditions.
Saffron flower extract powerful soothing properties restore comfort to dry skin, and revives skin radiance.
A trio of oils rich in omega 6, 7 and 9 (Cottonseed, Macadamia, Sunflower) reinforces the skin protective hydrolipidic film to restore suppleness and comfort to the skin.
An ultra-sensory, velvety texture with a non-shiny finish allows makeup to be used immediately.

name: Pure Luxury Cleansing Butter
short_description:
Peter Thomas Roth 24K Gold Pure Luxury Cleansing Butter has the following features:

Infused with pure 24K Gold in a solid-to-oil texture, this luxurious Cleansing Butter gently melts away makeup, dirt and impurities as it imparts an opulent glow.

Chamomile Butter and Honey deliver intense hydration as Kasturi Turmeric helps soothe the look of dry, sensitive skin.

Leaves skin silky soft, comfortable and revitalized while helping it look healthy and youthful.

Made from root vegetables, the accompanying Konjac sponge puffs up when wet to gently cleanse and exfoliate skin. Its unique teardrop shape allows for targeted, deep cleansing.

Suitable for all skin types, but especially dry.

name: Lotion (Enriched)
short_description:
KOSE Medicated Sekkisei Lotion (Enriched) has the following features:

A medicated lotion with oriental herbal extracts for supple, well-hydrated and snow-white skin.

Contains highly moisturizing ophiopogon tuber extract, rose myrtle extract and more. Richly hydrates the skin for enhanced translucency.

Contains two types of oleic acid derivatives for better permeation, allowing the lotion to penetrate easily into skin that is rough and dry.

Regulates the skin's moisture balance, treats dullness caused by dryness, and prevents the burning sensation caused by sunburn, snow-burn and other skin problems.

For the face, neck and body.

name: Multi-Perfection Creme Universal Texture
short_description:
Christian Dior Capture Totale Multi-Perfection Creme Universal Texture has the following features:
The Multi-Perfection Creme circumvents the laws of time and, for the 1st time, those of gravity.
This creme encourages the revitalization of the skin's precious 'springs': the mother cells at the origin of the deep contouring of the skin.
Superbly smoothing, resculpting and unifying, it tones the skin from its deepest layers to its surface.
The face is perfectly tautened and toned while all visible signs of aging - wrinkles, loss of firmness and radiance, and uneven skin tone - are corrected instantly and with every application.
Youthful beauty is brought to its pinnacle. Today and tomorrow.
With its fine, delicate, melt-in texture for unrivaled sensory delight, the Multi-Perfection Creme Universal texture delivers an instant embellishing effect and optimal comfort for all women.
Chez Dior.
Test in vitro.

Benefits:
Upon 1st application*, a visible improvement in skin quality: Suppler skin +97%, More beautiful skin +100%, Improved skin quality +100%, Complexion radiance +100%
After 1 month**, proven anti-gravity effectiveness: Ideal facial firmness +97%, More toned skin +98%, More elastic skin +97%
Global youthful beauty: Smoothed fine lines and wrinkles +85%, Firmer skin +97%, Redensified skin +95%
Test in-use. 60 women. Use of Multi-Perfection Creme Universal Texture - Results after one application.
Test in-use. 60 women. Use of Multi-Perfection Creme Universal Texture - Results after one month.

name: Conditioner
short_description:
Oribe Signature Conditioner has the following features:

Thanks to Hydrating Polymers, it revives youthful shine for lustrous, healthy locks and detangle for ease of combing throughout the day.

Thanks to Oribe Signature Complex (Watermelon, Lychee and Edelweiss Flower Extracts), it defends hair from oxidative stress, photoaging and the deterioration of natural keratin, while protecting from the drying, damaging and color-depleting effects of the elements.

Enriched with Macadamia Nut Seed Oil, from the Australian rainforest, it provides smoothing and antioxidant properties.

Thanks to Kaempferia Galanga Root Extract found in Southeast Asia, it delivers natural UV protection.

Infused with Keratin and Hydrolyzed Keratin, it helps strengthen damaged hair and protect the surface of the hair shaft while penetrating the cortex to provide anti-aging benefits, maintain hair strength and prevent UV degradation.

short_description:
Filorga Hydra-Hyal Intensive Hydrating Plumping Concentrate has the following features:
Highly concentrated in hyaluronic acid, it intensely replenishes the skin.
Infused with four types of Hyaluronic acid, it deeply penetrates the skin, instantly hydrating, smoothing and plumping it.
Thanks two plant-based boosters, it stimulates the production of hyaluronic acid in the dermis and epidermis in order to restore the skins natural reserves.
Infused with the combination of a skin-renewal ingredient and a revitalizing NCTF complex, it restores the skins fresh-looking, clear appearance.
The skin is immediately hydrated from within and its radiance and suppleness are restored. After 14 days, fine lines caused by dehydration are visibly reduced.
Suitable for dry to normal skin types.

name: Crescendo Progressive Night Peel
short_description:
Lancome Visionnaire Crescendo Progressive Night Peel has the following features:

Gently exfoliates skin surface cells and addresses multiple skin concerns: uneven skin texture, appearance of pores, wrinkles and fine lines, and dark spots.

Start with Phase 1 for the first 14 nights, formulated with 5% bio-acids such as fruit acids and quinoa husk extract that works to reduce the appearance of pores, improve skin's texture, and radiance.

Then, switch to Phase 2 for the last 14 nights. Formulated with 10% derma-acids, including 0.5% salicylic acid and 9.5% pure glycolic acid, this phase reduces the appearance of fine lines, wrinkles, and dark spots.

name: Fresh Pressed Daily Booster With Pure Vitamin C 10%
short_description:
Clinique Fresh Pressed Daily Booster with Pure Vitamin C 10% (For All Skin Types) has the following features:

Infused with highest concentration of fresh Vitamin C, it brightens, evens and retexturizes skin.

Just like fresh-pressed juice or vitamin helps you stay healthy on the inside.

Designed as a daily supplement to visibly rejuvenate skin from the outside, which is a simple, seamless alternative to reinvigorate your de-aging routine.

Designed as a stay-fresh packaging, it isolates the pure Vitamin C until activation, maintaining its freshness and full power for maximum results.

short_description:

Keeps eyes looking younger, fresher, brighter by visibly minimizing first lines and signs of fatigue including dark circles and puffiness.
With refreshing, cream-gel texture, it instantly soothes eye contours.
Enhances drainage so eyes appear instantly luminous and more youthful-looking with an ultra-cold, cryo-metallic application tip.
Visibly smooths fine lines around the eye contour, and revives and brightens the eye area.

Satisfaction test  100 women aged 30-39 4 weeks.

name: Colour 2-In-1 Prime & Colour Correct Face-Eyes-Lips
short_description:
Christian Dior Fix It Colour 2-In-1 Prime & Colour Correct Face-Eyes-Lips has the following features:
Dior invents its first multipurpose colour concealer: 1 stick, 2 textures, 3 application areas, 4 expert shades, targeting and neutralizing the colour imperfections of the complexion and around the eye and lip contours with the inspiration of backstage makeup techniques.

Blue (100):
Target the dullness.
This lilac-blue is an expert on yellow-toned Caucasian skins and Asian skins by evening out exhausted complexions for extra radiance.
Dab on the light-catching areas such as the forehead and the tips of the cheeks to give them an instantly fresh and rested look.

Apricot (200):
Ideal for matte or tanned complexions.
Tones down greyness, diminishes dark spots and corrects areas of hyperpigmentation and dark circles, while evening out dark skins.

Yellow (300):
Targets the dark spots and dark circles.
A must-have for light skins to erase violet-tinted shadows, from blood vessels to circles under the eyes.
Neutralizes lips with a blue hue to bring out the real colour of the lipstick.

Green (400):
Target the redness.
Used in light touches to fade blood vessels and flushed areas to target light complexions and rosy skins.

name: Abeille Royale Replenishing Eye Cream
short_description:
Guerlain Abeille Royale Replenishing Eye Cream has the following features:

Infused with high concentration of Exclusive Guerlain Royal Jelly, it helps restore, smoothen and repair the skin density around eye area.

Lightens the wrinkles and fine lines around eye area while reducing the dark circles and sagginess for a tightening effect.

Helps strengthen the supporting skin tissue to give a remarkable remodeling effect and greater density to the eyes with its exceptional restorative and nutritive qualities, particularly adapted to the needs of this extremely delicate and fragile area.

Wrinkles are reduced by 22%.*

Skin density around eyes is increased 39%.***

The firmness of skin around eyes is increased by 29%.***

Enriched with exceptional nutrients and a blend of carbohydrates, proteins, lipids and vitamins, the eye cream offers exceptional benefits for the skin.

Rich in amino acids, trace elements and high in fructose-content, this honey offers the essential ingredients that are vital in the repair process of skin tissue.

*In vitro tests on ingredients.

**Instrumental test carried out on 16 women, immediate results noted after application.

***Clinical assessment carried out on 32 women, after two months of twice-daily application.

name: Replenishing Cleansing Oil
short_description:
Elizabeth Arden Ceramide Replenishing Cleansing Oil has the following features:
An excellent solution for both removing makeup, even waterproof mascara and eyeliner, and dissolving impurities from skin.
Nourishes skin with essential lipids to leave it feeling clean, soft, and smooth.
Fuses the antioxidant and conditioning properties of Apricot, Safflower and Olive Oils to dissolve cosmetic debris and sebum, while repairing the skins barrier layer.
Does not leave behind an oily residue or clog pores, resulting in a fresh, healthy looking complexion that is never dry or greasy.

name: Healthy Glow Foundation SPF25 / PA++
short_description:
Chanel Les Beiges Healthy Glow Foundation SPF25 / PA++ has the following features:
An invisible foundation that creates a natural healthy glow by giving skin the radiance of a day spent outdoors, while protecting it from harsh environmental conditions.
The soft and comfortable texture glides over the skin and melts away. It adapts to the shape of the face and invisibly follows its every movement.
The texture becomes imperceptible and allows the skin to breathe freely, creating an immaculately even, bright and delicate complexion.
Kalanchoe extract and UV filters protect the skin from harsh environmental conditions.
Healthy Glow Booster mineral pigments instantly deliver a dazzling healthy glow. Together with Soft Focus powders, they even out the complexion and enhance it, creating a sheer finish.
With its hyaluronic acid derivative, the texture provides an instant sensation of hydration and comfort that lasts all day long.

name: Midnight Secret Recovery Treatment
short_description:
Guerlain Midnight Secret Late Night Recovery Treatment has the following features:

Guerlain Research has developed a complex whose active ingredients allow your skin to recover more quickly during the night to fight against signs of tiredness on the face.

Boosts the microcirculation and cell oxygenation and offers a decongesting effect, while limiting the harmful effects of free radicals.*

With a few drops of this ""sleep elixir"" and a few hours' rest, traces of fatigue seem to miraculously disappear and your complexion looks radiant.

85% noticed that this treatment helps restore the complexion's freshness in the morning after the excesses of the night before, which helps get rid of the dullness, creating a fresher, brighter and more even complexion.**

*In vitro test.

**In use test, 33 people.

name: Orchidee Imperiale The Cream
short_description:
Guerlain Orchidee Imperiale Exceptional Complete Care The Cream (4th Generation) has the following features:
Infused with precious diamond powder to the formula. This rare raw material helps capture light energy and diffuse for an instant sophisticated radiance.
New Cell Respiration™ technology delivers superior efficacy inside the skin. It regulates cellular respiration and combats hypoxia* or oxygen deficiency, a phenomenon that increases with age.
It helps minimize visible signs of aging like wrinkles, fine lines fade.
Features a floral scent with hints of Orchid, notes of Rose, White Musk and precious Cedar Wood.
Promotes +44% hydration. (1)
Minimizes 23% wrinkles. (2)
Promotes +15% firmness. (3)
Promotes +18% luminosity. (4)
100% of women reported skin is more beautiful, the complexion even and radiant. (5)
*In vitro tests on ingredient
(1) Instrumental test, 11 women, results 24 hrs after application.
(2) Instrumental test, 15 women, results just after application.
(3) Clinical test by a dermatologist, 33 women, results after 1 month.
(4) Clinical test by a dermatologist, 33 women, results after the first application.
(5) Satisfaction test, 60 Chinese women, results after 1 month.

name: Vital-Perfection Wrinklelift Mask
short_description:
Shiseido Vital-Perfection Wrinklelift Mask has the following features:

This eye mask delivers delicate retinol and Shiseido VP8 deep into the epidermis, effectively improving visible wrinkles with RetinoVP8 technology.

Protects volatile retinol from light and oxygen with the special airtight packaging process.

Fits over the facial areas with the unique flower petal shape that are most active in facial expressions in which wrinkles tend to appear.

The skin is protected with a veil of hydration for a 24-hour moisturizing effect.

With continued use, it helps reduce loss of resilience, visible dark spots, and dull, yellow tone.

name: Dermatologist Solutions Clearly Corrective Dark Spot Solution
short_description:
Kiehl's Dermatologist Solutions Clearly Corrective Dark Spot Solution with exclusive activated C, Clearly Corrective is a fast-acting serum that evens skin tone and diminishes dark spots to impart overall radiance and luminosity to the skin.



With continued daily usage, Clearly Corrective helps to prevent the formation of future dark spots and other skin discolorations.

In as little as 2 weeks, 55% of women clinically demonstrated a significant reduction in dark spot intensity.




In 4 weeks, 69% of women clinically demonstrated a continued reduction in dark spots intensity and 73% of women showed a significant reduction in acne scarring. Reduction in other skin discolorations was clinically evident among 69% of women.




In 8 weeks, 87% of women clinically demonstrated more uniform skin tone to deliver breakthrough clarity.

name: Supreme Refining Cream
short_description:
Diam Beaute Supreme Refining Cream has the following features:
A highly effective, luxurious cream infused with potent ingredients to smooth wrinkles, restore radiance and moisture to the skin, revealing a vividly renewed, sculpted, luminous and younger complexion.
It contains exquisite Black Diamond Truffle with major skincare benefits as its main ingredient. It has 18 kinds of amino acids (including 8 essential amino acids), which are effective in reducing fine lines and wrinkles.
Rich in vitamins, antioxidants and trace elements, Black Truffle promotes skin renewal for a more radiant, translucent and youthful complexion.
Extra-fine diamond powder penetrates into the skin to stimulate skin cell renewal, restoring glowing, younger-looking skin.
24K Gold helps revitalize skin, improve dullness, and promote skin metabolism to fight against free radicals and delay aging.
SEPILIFT one of the most powerful patented anti-aging ingredients in the 21st century triggers collagen remodeling and collagen fiber contraction to deliver instant lifting and wrinkle-smoothing effects as well as excellent hydrating capability.

short_description:
EVE LOM White Brightening Cream has the following features:
This innovative hydrating cream combines brightening powers of Dermapep with anti-oxidant actives to correct hyperpigmentation and boost radiance to reveal a bright and even-toned complexion.
Infused with Rose Otto Oil, it hydrates, restores skin structure and combats oxidative stresses that cause premature aging and dark spots.
Suitable for all skin types.
Especially recommend for those with pigmentation or uneven skin tone and lack of radiance, or to prevent early signs of aging.

name: Herbal Gel
short_description:
KOSE Sekkisei Herbal Gel has the following features:

A multifunctional gel for translucent, smooth, and snow-like skin.

Provides 6 skincare benefits: hydrating, improving skin texture, correcting dullness, smoothing roughness, firming skin, restoring radiance.

Formulated with extracts of fermented coix seed, angelica, melothria, loquat, and mugwort, it improves dry, dull skin and allows it to radiate light from within, adding translucency.

Combines the effects of an emulsion, serum, cream, massage and mask in one.

The moisturizing texture melts into the stratum corneum easily, allowing moisture to flow through skin, making it plump and supple.

Formulated with a non-sticky oil that blends right in without any stickiness or oiliness.

name: Premier Cru La Creme Riche
short_description:
CAUDALIE Premier Cru La Creme Riche (Dry Skin) has the following features:

This luxurious cream delivers ultimate anti-aging benefits for younger skin with patented ingredients combining the rare and effective elements of vines and grapes.

Resveratrol promotes the production of collagen and elastin, increases the thickness of the epidermis, smoothes the wrinkles from inside out, and elongates the lifespan of young cells to restore the skin's radiance.

Contains Viniferine extracted from grape vines, which boosts 62 times more whitening effect than vitamin C, effectively decelerating the formation of pigmentation for more radiant and even-toned skin.

Polyphenols are powerful antioxidants that help fight against free radicals and repel most causes of skin aging.

It contains a high concentration of Eleutherococcus Senticosus extract and various precious beauty essences to delay skin aging and deliver the anti-oxidizing effects.
Multiple layers of phospholipid capsule technology help the nourishing ingredients penetrate thoroughly into the skin, revitalizing skin energy and tension.
Prevents fine lines around the eye area caused by dryness, restoring firmness, suppleness and youth to skin.

name: Genaissance De  The Serum Essence
short_description:
La Mer Genaissance De La Mer The Serum Essence has the following features:
This age-transcending serum essence was inspired when a scientist at the Max Huber Research Labs discovered crystals forming in a beaker of Miracle Broth
Extraordinarily pure, the Crystal Miracle Broth is slow-crafted in extremely small batches to reach its ultimate potency.
This advanced broth infuses skin with the life-generating energies of the sea, helping it visibly renew from within.
In moments, genesis begins. Day after day, skin is infused with a new look of life. Contours appear lifted and firmed, pores are refined and skin becomes plumper, suppler and more translucent.

name: Teint Couture Balm Blurring Foundation Balm SPF15 - PA++
short_description:
Givenchy Teint Couture Balm Blurring Foundation Balm SPF15 - PA++ has the following features:
A complexion-enhancing veil that blurs and brightens your skin tone.
Formulated with blurring technology to smooth and unify your complexion and create a subtle second skin effect.
Light-reflecting diamond powder pigments enrich your skin tone with a gorgeous glow, resulting in a beautifully fresh finish for up to 12 hours.
Light & Blur complex erases the look of imperfections on your skin, whilst diffusing fine lines and wrinkles.
Hydro-magnets work to lock in moisture to your complexion, preventing your skin from feeling and looking dehydrated.
Antioxidants, vitamin E and jasmine flower nourish your skin whilst protecting your skin from free radicals.
This delicate formula melts into your skin with a non-greasy feel.

name: Advanced Night Repair Intensive Recovery Ampoules
short_description:
Estee Lauder Advanced Night Repair Intensive Recovery Ampoules has the following features:

The night repair expert revolutionizes nighttime skin care regimen once again and introduces Advanced Night Repair Intensive Recovery Ampoules.

Micro ampoules. Mega impact. This powerful recovery concentrate calms and rapidly renews the look of over-stressed skin, helping to strengthen its resistance against future assaults.

This treatment oil features ChronoluxAI technology to help reduce visible irritation and synchronize the look of skin.

Effectively reduces skin problems and redness caused by irritation and restores healthier, younger and more radiant skin.

After just one ampoule, 92% of women said their skin felt calmed and soothed the next morning.* Skin looked more radiant and healthy.

Apply it over Advanced Night Repair Serum and in just 2 weeks, the improvement in skin protective barrier strength is more than doubled.**

Revolutionizes how you repair at night. Helps your skin recover the healthy, luminous look of youth.

*Consumer testing on a total of 567 women with stressed skin.

**Compared with using Advanced Night Repair Serum alone.

name: Rouge Interdit Vinyl Extreme Shine Lipstick Illicit Color
short_description:
Givenchy Rouge Interdit Vinyl Extreme Shine Lipstick Illicit Color has the following features:
The new lip beauty secret for women. A lipstick so addictive and so illicit, it's almost forbidden.
A unique lipstick that dares everything: extreme shine, impactful shades, and an obvious plump-up effect.
It is more than a lipstick, it is an attitude. It provides the signature look for beauty addicts who are not afraid to assert their own rules of style.
Combines rare black rose oil for extreme moisture with a silicone resin for a vinyl-like shine.
An amazing stretch formula for lips with tantalizing curves.
Lips instantly appear fuller and smoother with intense color.
The slick case has metallic satin ribbon inspired by the House fashion designs.

name: Base Perfecting Pearl Anti Dullness Mythical Skin-Perfecting Base
short_description:
Guerlain Meteorites Base Perfecting Pearl Anti Dullness Mythical Skin-Perfecting Base has the following features:
The fresh gel texture melt with the rosy pearls to give skin a plumpy finish while a combination of absorbent powders and a special polymer neutralizes excess sebum and helps conceal blemishes for a long-lasting matt complexion that gradually becomes more even with each application.
Thanks to the Stardust technology, a diamond powder encapsulated in micro spheres, light is reflected in a new direction to create soft-focus perfecting halo.
Multi-coloured pearlescent flecks maximise the diffusion of light and delicately correct the complexion thanks to the unique mix of colours, signature of the Meteorites range.

name: Bright Eye Serum
short_description:
COSME DECORTE AQ MW Bright Eye Serum has the following features:

Contains selected moisturizers that prevent fine wrinkles and make the eye area look more lively.

Stemrise iPG1, developed through research into PG cells associated with firmness of the epidermis, provides supple firmness to the eye area.

The dewy fresh texture, like a condensed serum, spreads beautifully across skin. Makes the skin clear and moist, immediately after application.

Mucin2some and double peptides quickly work on skin problems caused by external stress and brighten the eye area.

The spatula with the gentle massager gently takes care of shadows under the eyes that are caused by poor blood circulation or poor excretion of waste, and dryness and dullness in the eye area.

The cool feel of the massager refreshes the eye area to improve the benefits of eye care.

A relaxing blend of essential oils and the delicate scent of sandalwood, specially tailored for use in the delicate eye area.

name: Night Multi-Rejuvenating Nighttime Serum-In-Cream
short_description:
Philosophy Ultimate Miracle Worker Night Multi-Rejuvenating Nighttime Serum-In-Cream has the following features:
For the first time, it has been combined the concentrated power of a serum with the nourishing benefits of a cream to help dramatically reduce the signs of present and past skin-aging, while you sleep.
The exclusive formula targets all major signs of aging including lines, wrinkles, firmness, texture, pores and radiance.
Its patented technologies and ingredients are proven to help improve skin regeneration and epidermal repair, while helping skin rebuild its natural collagen and rejuvenate its appearance layer by layer.
In just 3 nights you will wake up to a dewy, vibrant and more-rested complexion.*
In 2 weeks 97% of women had noticeably healthier-looking skin.**
100% dramatically improved the texture and firmness of their skin.**
In 4 weeks: the length, width and depth of wrinkles was significantly reduced.**
More than half of women agreed that they had their best-looking skin in years even compared to receiving professional skin treatments.*
*Self-assessment study, 42 women ages 45-65.
**Independent clinical study, 32 women ages 45-65.

name: Black Tea Firming Overnight Mask
short_description:
Fresh Black Tea Firming Overnight Mask has the following features:
An intensely moisturizing treatment that works in sync with the natural nighttime recovery process to achieve a lifted, firmer look by morning.
The mask has a corset-like effect on the skin, giving the appearance of a visibly more defined, contoured complexion.
A proprietary complex of black tea ferment, black tea extract, blackberry leaf extract, and lychee seed extract is proven to inhibit damaging free radicals** and helps to improve skin elasticity.
Belle De Nuit extract, known as nature's nocturnal flower, helps to soothe and rebalance the skin.
Peptides help firm the skin and visibly defy the signs of gravity.
Hyaluronic acid helps attract and maintain moisture to enhance suppleness.
97% noticed their skin looked visibly healthier after 1 month.
94% felt their skin was more supple and radiant after 2 weeks.
94% said their skin looked revitalized after 1 month.
91% noticed diminished signs of fatigue after 2 weeks.
88% saw improved elasticity and firmness after 1 month.
*Consumer test on 32 subjects during 28 days
**Test in vitro

short_description:

Modest: A fresh, rich berry pink color.

Curious: A bright wearable golden orange.

short_description:

name: Concentrated Recovery PowerFoil Mask
short_description:
Estee Lauder Advanced Night Repair Concentrated Recovery PowerFoil Mask has the following features:

A true industry revolution, this innovative mask combines advanced technology with the 65 global award-winning Advanced Night Repair Serum.

Starting tonight, reset the look of your skin after the visible stresses of modern life with this innovative weekly treatment mask. Instantly, skin looks fresher, renewed.

Esstee Lauder worldwide first high-performance foil-backed sheet mask creates a protective barrier, allowing potent technologies to penetrate fast and deep within skin's surface and helping to lock in moisture.

Each treatment delivers a surge of liquid revitalization, immersing skin in nearly half a bottle's worth of Advanced Night Repair's exclusive Chronolux and 2X Hyaluronic Acid.

The first of its kind system features an inside matrix that releases the concentrated treatment, while the outside foil matrix helps seal in potent liquid and enhances penetration 25X faster than a traditional cotton sheet mask.

Provides long-lasting hydration for a week with each mask.

Experience an ultimate infusion of youthful moisture.

name: Liposome Treatment Liquid
short_description:
COSME DECORTE Liposome Treatment Liquid has the following features:
After 12 years of intensive research and development, COSME DECORTE developed a new liposome using two varieties of phospholipids and released Liposome Treatment Liquid.
These liposomes measuring just 0.1-0.2 microns allow beauty ingredients to penetrate into the stratum corneum easily.
Beauty ingredients such as Loquat Leaf extract and Butchers Broom Root extract are encapsulated in these liposomes in a time-released manner. Use it morning and evening to help moisturize the skin for 24 hours. It gives firmness, translucency and long-lasting moisture to the skin like never before.

name: Genoptics Aura Essence
short_description:
SK-II GenOptics Aura Essence has the following features:
This all-new upgraded whitening formula contains Pixel white ,De-melano P3C, Japanese UME extract, Concentrated PITERA and new ingredients including US Prunus Extract and Inositol. They work together to help improve lackluster and dull skin, reduces spots and UV-induced melanin for a radiant complexion.
After using for 8 weeks, it significantly improves dull skin, increases melanin-blocking substances, and reduces colored pigments deep in the skin for clearer, more radiant and translucent skin.
Effectively reduces spots deep in the skin and restores diamond-like radiance and brightness to skin.
Lightweight texture, feels hydrating on the skin and instantly illuminates skin.
Smart dropper design allows the dropper to get the recommended dosage automatically every time, as you twist and open the bottle, and just the right amount for the whole face.
GenOptics Spot Essence is ideal for day use, while GenOptics Aura Essence is suitable for night use. Using both products will complement each other and achieve even better results.

name: Concentrated Recovery PowerFoil Mask
short_description:
Estee Lauder Advanced Night Repair Concentrated Recovery PowerFoil Mask has the following features:

A true industry revolution, this innovative mask combines advanced technology with the 65 global award-winning Advanced Night Repair Serum.

Starting tonight, reset the look of your skin after the visible stresses of modern life with this innovative weekly treatment mask. Instantly, skin looks fresher, renewed.

Esstee Lauder worldwide first high-performance foil-backed sheet mask creates a protective barrier, allowing potent technologies to penetrate fast and deep within skin's surface and helping to lock in moisture.

Each treatment delivers a surge of liquid revitalization, immersing skin in nearly half a bottle's worth of Advanced Night Repair's exclusive Chronolux and 2X Hyaluronic Acid.

The first of its kind system features an inside matrix that releases the concentrated treatment, while the outside foil matrix helps seal in potent liquid and enhances penetration 25X faster than a traditional cotton sheet mask.

Provides long-lasting hydration for a week with each mask.

Experience an ultimate infusion of youthful moisture.

name: Multi-Perfection Creme Rich Texture
short_description:
Christian Dior Capture Totale Multi-Perfection Creme Rich Texture has the following features:

The Multi-Perfection Creme circumvents the laws of time and, for the 1st time*, those of gravity.

This creme encourages the revitalization of the skin's precious ""springs"": the mother cells at the origin of the deep contouring of the skin**.

Superbly smoothing, resculpting and unifying, it tones the skin from its deepest layers to its surface.

The face is perfectly tautened and toned while all visible signs of aging - wrinkles, loss of firmness and radiance, and uneven skin tone - are corrected instantly and with every application.

Youthful beauty is brought to its pinnacle. Today and tomorrow.

Intensely delicate, the Multi-Perfection Creme Light Texture is an airy gel-creme combining instant comfort and freshness that irrigates youthful skin. Its transparent and airy texture fuses with the skin and delivers perfect comfort, even in hot and humid climates.

*Chez Dior.

** Test in vitro.



Benefits:

Upon 1st application*, a visible improvement in skin quality: Softer skin +97%, Suppler skin +97% .

After 1 month**, proven anti-gravity effectiveness: Optimal face hold +75%, Lifted facial contours +78%, Toned skin +94%, More elastic skin +88%.

Global youthful beauty**: Reduced fine lines and wrinkles +75%, Firmer skin +81%, Redensified skin +84%.

*Test in-use. 32 women. Use of Multi-Perfection Creme Rich Texture - Results after 1 application.

**Test in-use. 32 women. Use of Multi-Perfection Creme Rich Texture - Results after one month.

short_description:

Provides a three-dimensional treatment that contains a unique combination of ingredients to dramatically improve severe signs of intrinsic aging around the eyes. Helps diminish dark circles, puffiness, and effects of glycation.
Contains a complex of flavonoids and synergistic peptides to diminishes the appearance of dark circles, reinforces firmness and tone in the eye area and diminishes under-eye bags.

name: Liquid Minerals™ A Foundation - Warm Silk
short_description:
Jane Iredale Liquid Minerals™ A Foundation is a light-reflecting, soft-focus foundation with beads encapsulating skin-nourishing ingredients that work in a time-released action. The spheres include Hyaluronate Acid and Olive Squalene that are entrapped by seaweed lipids, which are then suspended in an Aloe Vera and Lavender Flower gel.


Suitable for all skin types, Jane Iredale Liquid Minerals™ A Foundation makes skin look more youthful, diminishes the appearance of lines and wrinkles, minimizes pores, and evens out skin tone. It has a natural pH of 6 and is so perfectly balanced that it needs no pH adjusters.


As Jane Iredale Liquid Minerals™ A Foundation is applied and worked into the skin, the body temperature breaks down the liposomes so that they can release their actives in a prolonged time-release action for the ultimate in skin health and protection.


Warm Silk - light color with peach undertones

name: Super Restorative Day Cream
short_description:
Clarins Super Restorative Day Cream (For Very Dry Skin), with its illuminating, lifting and replenishing formula, helps restore elasticity to mature skin challenged by natural hormonal changes due to the ageing process. Clarins has discovered that a cell in the dermis called Fibroblast plays a key part in maintaining youthful skin.



When the function of Fibroblast is disrupted, the skin ageing process speeds up. Clarins Super Restorative Day Cream (For Very Dry Skin) is infused with Harungana plant extract, which can reactivate deprived Fibroblast and stimulate growth of collagen fibres. Combined with new generation line-filling pearls, skin appears plumped and tighter immediately, and deep wrinkles are reduced.



Clarins Super Restorative Day Cream (For Very Dry Skin) is also added with Vitamin C derivative that inhibits melanin production to minimize the appearance of age spots, thus achieving a more illuminated and even complexion. Hyaluronic Acid and Shea Butter moisturize skin, restoring a comfortable, supple feel.

name: Fortifying Mint Toothpaste
short_description:
Dr. Hauschka Med Teeth Fortifying Mint Toothpaste has the following features:

Strong gums and thorough oral hygiene are essential for healthy teeth. It is therefore important to stabilize the oral flora in order to prevent harmful bacteria from growing in the first place.

Regular brushing with a fortifying toothpaste helps to prevent plaque (bacterial film on the teeth), as well as the tartar, gum problems and caries that may result from it.

Dr.Hauschka Med Teeth Fortifying Mint Toothpaste has been proven to reduce inflammation quickly, fortifying the gums and promoting a balanced, healthy oral flora.

Astringent extracts of horse chestnut fortify the gums and help to prevent gum bleeding.

The cleansing properties of natural essential oils help to keep breath fresh.

name: Day Cream (All Skin Types)
short_description:
Clarins Super Restorative Day Cream (All Skin Types), with its illuminating, lifting and replenishing formula, helps restore elasticity to mature skin challenged by natural hormonal changes due to the ageing process. Clarins has discovered that a cell in ther dermis called the Fibroblast plays a key part in maintaining youthful skin.



When there is a lack of hormones, its functions are disrupted and the skin ageing process speeds up. Clarins Super Restorative Day Cream (All Skin Types) is infused with Harungana plant extract, which can reactivate deprived Fibroblas and stimulate growth of collagen fibres. Combined with new generation, line-filling pearls, skin appears plumped and tighter immediately, and deep wrinkles are reduced.



Clarins Super Restorative Day Cream (All Skin Types) is also added with Vitamin C derivative that inhibits melanin production to minimize the appearance of age spots, thus achieving a more illuminated and even complexion. Hyaluronic Acid and Shea Butter moisturize skin, restoring a comfortable, supple feel. Suitable for all skin types.

name: Matte Radiance Baked Powder
short_description:
Laura Mercier Matte Radiance Baked Powder wakes up the skin, and provide natural color with a radiant, healthy glow for a flawless, no-makeup look.



Laura Mercier Matte Radiance Baked Powder wakes combines with an ultrasmooth baked formula that provides natural color with soft radiance to the skin for a healthy, 'bonne mine' glow. Bronze shades impart a matte finish and a hint of warmth for a flawless, no-makeup finish.



More benefits:

Modern, multidimensional matte finish with a hint of soft luminosity.

Sheer, buildable coverage lets you customize your glow.

Applies smoothly onto skin and blends effortlessly for a natural look and feel.

Ultra-lightweight formula, feels weightless on skin.

Smooth, silky, velvety texture feels comfortable on skin.

Longwearing formula lasts up to 8 hours.

Color stays true without oxidizing for an even finish.

Nondusty, nondrying formula.

Dermatologist-tested. Suitable for all skin types, even sensitive.

Bronzer: Using the Bronzer Brush, lightly tap on top of domed bronzer, making sure to cover all edges of brush with product. Tap off excess product. Using the tapered head of the brush, apply to areas where the sun naturally hits, like cheeks, nose, brow bone, forehead and chin, creating a natural """"sun-kissed"""" look.



Highlighter: Using the Angled Cheek Colour brush, lightly tap onto domed highlighter covering all edges of brush. Tap off excess product. Using the tapered head of the brush, apply over the high points of the face: cheekbones, center of nose, cupid's bow and top of forehead.

name: Shampoo
short_description:
Orofluido Shampoo cleanses delicately, conserving the hair's structure and leaving it light and incredibly shiny. Orofluido Shampoo is the beauty treatment for all hair types that delicately cleanses to leave hair light and shiny. A pure luxuriance that envelops the hair.



Orofluido is pure sensuality, a celebration of the senses. The mystery of the fragrance of amber, the fascination for the most precious natural oils. The luxury of gold. A beauty ritual for all types of hair. Its delicious amber fragrance with a vanilla foundation will transport you into a fascinating world of oriental perfume.



An exquisite mixture of natural oils:

Argan oil: liquid gold for your hair

Extracted from the seeds of the Argania spinosa fruit, Argan oil is rich in vitamin E and essential fatty oils, similar in composition to our own skin. It strengthens hair and makes it extremely light and incredibly silky.




Linseed oil: instant shine

The seeds of the linen plant are the source of a precious oil which seals and smoothes the hair cuticle, providing uniformity and control. The result is hair that captures and reflects the light, giving it a spectacular shine.




Cyperus oil: pure silk to the touch

Cyperus is a plant that has been cultivated in Egypt for more than 4,000 years. It is the source of an oil with a high content of fatty acids and tocopherol, which give natural protection against free radicals. It provides softness and volume, leaving hair manageable, smooth and flexible.

name: Liposome Essence 40ml
short_description:
COSME DECORTE Moisture Liposome Essence improves moisture absorption for your skin. It penetrates surface skin cells completely and continuously moisturizes dry, chapped or problem skin. Spreads with a moist touch and makes your skin feel silky smooth and works all night long so the next morning you can actually feel the smoothness from deep inside your skin.



Consisting of very 'determined' high-IQ micro-capsules that know how and where to go, COSME DECORTE Moisture Liposome Essence aids to strengthen areas of deficiency and restores damaged skin cells. It is a magic microcapsule - with the swiftness and great reflexes of a first-class athlete!



Each liposome is composed of as many as 10 to 20 layers, peeling off one by one in a time-release manner. As each layer peels off, a fresh portion of beautifying agents is released into the skin over time. Conventional moisturizers manage to moisturize the skin only at the time of application.



Simply because it is so powerfully effective, there is no need to add impurities to reinforce its capability. Oil-free. Alcohol-free. Suitable for all skin types, even on sensitive skins. And for all seasons of the year.

short_description:
Hydra-Flash Formule Intensive incorporates a powerful complex of natural molecules, natural plant extracts (Rice, Sesame) and essential oils (Marjoram, Rosewood), selected for their potential to dramatically enhance cell cohesion and encourage improved moisture binding in the outer skin layers. The result is super-power hydration that lasts over time.
